steps.html:
Choose the first line in <var>possible lines</var> greater than or equal to the <a data-link-type="dfn" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid-3/#auto-placement-cursor" id="ref-for-auto-placement-cursor">auto-placement cursor</a>
					as the item’s position in the <a data-link-type="dfn" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid-3/#grid-axis" id="ref-for-grid-axis①⑨">grid axis</a>;
					or if there are none such, choose the first one.
